definition: Pineapple mealybug wilt-associated virus 3 ORF1a and RNA dependent RNA polymerase (RdRp) genes, partial cds; p6 gene, complete sequence; and mall hydrophobic 5.65 kDa protein, heat shock 70-like protein (hsp70h), 61.0 kDa protein (p61), 28.8 kDa putative coat protein (CP), and 24.1 kDa protein (p24) genes, complete cds.
